Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm having some issues with my recent billing statement from the bowling alley.

I'm sorry to hear about that! I'd be happy to help you sort this out. May I have your name, please?

Sure, it's Jamie.

Thank you, Jamie. Can you please provide your account number so I can pull up your billing information? The account number should be eight digits long.

Of course, it's one two three four five six seven eight.

Great, I have your account pulled up. Could you also verify your email address associated with the account, just to make sure I have the correct details?

Yes, it's jamie@example.com.

Perfect, everything seems to be in order on our end. Can you tell me what issue you're experiencing so we can resolve it?

I noticed that I was charged twice for the same bowling session last week.

Thank you for letting us know, Jamie. I will investigate this right away and ensure any duplicate charges are corrected. Our billing department will reach out to you within two business days. Thank you for your patience.

Thank you, Alex. I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for bringing this to our attention and for your understanding. Have a great day!
